        {
            "title": "伊朗外長稱新任最高領袖沒有任何問題",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com — 伊朗外交部長阿拉格奇(Abbas Araqchi)表示,伊朗新任最高領袖莫吉塔巴·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"哈梅內伊\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:哈梅內伊;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/哈梅內伊\">哈梅內伊</a>(Mojtaba Khamenei)沒有任何問題,並駁斥了美國聲稱他在最近的襲擊中受傷的說法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在週六接受MS Now採訪時,阿拉格奇駁斥了美國國防部長皮特·赫格塞斯(Pete Hegseth)的言論。赫格塞斯週五曾表示,哈梅內伊受傷並\"可能毀容\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈梅內伊在其父親阿亞圖拉·阿里·哈梅內伊(Ayatollah Ali Khamenei)於美國-以色列聯合襲擊中身亡後繼任,自上任以來一直未公開露面,引發了外界對其健康狀況的猜測。伊朗官員多次表示,儘管衝突持續,他仍有能力履行職責。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-167b8eac-fb75-3086-aa26-65621c5e9f81-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在地區戰爭不斷升級的背景下,伊朗與美國之間的緊張局勢依然高漲,雙方的矛盾聲明也反映了這一點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E7%A8%B1%E6%96%B0%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-181744391.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-15 02:25:40",
